        "content": "<p>ignatz opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13559\">PR #13559</a> from <code>ignatz:v45-timers</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Suggesting a patch version v45.0.1</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>If this work has been discussed elsewhere, please include a link to that   conversation. If it was discussed in an issue, just mention \"issue #...\".</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13507\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13507</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Explain why this change is needed. If the details are in an issue already,  this can be brief.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Subjectively for my use-cases this falls into the correctness bucket of the release process:</p>\n<p>\"Patch releases of Wasmtime will only be issued for security and critical correctness issues for on-by-default behavior in supported releases\"</p>\n<p>Thanks!</p>\n</blockquote>",
